    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8 era. The powerplant, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, has undergone documented preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator services. The chassis integrity is flawless, retaining the factory-original carbon fiber roof for a reduced center of gravity. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. The exterior displays consistent paint depth across all panels, while the suspension geometry remains true, complemented by fully functional Electronic Damper Control (EDC). This is a collector-grade specimen with an immaculate undercarriage and zero interior bolster wear.",
      "price": 48500.0,
