    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This single-owner gem has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, showroom luster with a professional ceramic coating and is entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic feature and safety system functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a full service history exclusively through the dealership, with a major service recently completed including a fresh set of high-performance tires. The engine bay is spotless, reflecting the obsessive care this vehicle has received. This is a collector-grade example for a discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection. Sold with all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive folder of maintenance receipts.",
